ActBank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of JOCELYNE PELCHAT of Sutton, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada to hold office, during good behaviour, for a term ending February 28, 2007, in the place of Paul Massicotte, who has resigned.
